      "content": "but how would they even know i'm in the kitchen specifically to name the wifi that? it feels like they're trying to mess with my head. if it was just a coincidence about the router being in that room, why would they use that specific phrasing? is there any way they could actually be using the wifi signal to detect motion or something? like, could the signal strength be used as a sensor?",
